{"word":"λαλέω","slug":"λαλέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>λαλέω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Skt.\">Skt.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ assoc.\">assoc.</a>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘make a sound’, <b>to sound,</b> in imagery of a trumpet blast <b><a href='B:730 4:1'>Rv 4:1</a>;</b> of thunder <b><a href='B:730 10:4'>10:4</a>;</b> of blood<b> <a href='B:650 11:4'>Hb 11:4</a>; <a href='B:650 12:24'>12:24</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘make a statement’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> speak (about), talk (about) <a href='B:470 10:20'>Mt 10:20</a>; <a href='B:470 12:34'>12:34a</a></b> and throughout the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a>. Of restored ability to speak or articulate <b><a href='B:470 9:33'>Mt 9:33</a>; <a href='B:480 7:35'>Mk 7:35</a>, <a href='B:480 7:37'>37</a>; <a href='B:490 1:64'>Lk 1:64</a>.</b> As noun <b><a href='B:510 13:45'>Ac 13:45</a>; <a href='B:510 16:14'>16:14</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> tell <a href='B:470 9:18'>Mt 9:18</a>; <a href='B:470 13:3'>13:3</a>; <a href='B:480 2:2'>Mk 2:2</a>; <a href='B:490 2:20'>Lk 2:20</a>; <a href='B:500 8:25'>J 8:25</a>, <a href='B:500 8:40'>40</a>; <a href='B:500 14:25'>14:25</a>; <a href='B:500 16:1'>16:1</a>; <a href='B:510 9:6'>Ac 9:6</a>; <a href='B:510 27:25'>27:25</a>.</b> As noun <b><a href='B:490 1:45'>Lk 1:45</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp> say, utter <a href='B:470 10:19'>Mt 10:19</a>; <a href='B:470 12:34'>12:34b</a>, 36; <a href='B:500 18:20'>J 18:20</a>; <a href='B:500 19:10'>19:10</a>; <a href='B:520 3:19'>Ro 3:19</a>; <a href='B:530 15:34'>1 Cor 15:34</a>; <a href='B:540 4:13'>2 Cor 4:13</a>; <a href='B:540 7:14'>7:14</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:λακτίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:λαλιά\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}